---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'March 13, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="OPX Terms of Service — the rules and conditions for using opxhq.com."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-brand-muted mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using opxhq.com ("the Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use the Site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">2. Content & Medical Disclaimer</h2>
        <div class="bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-600/30 rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="text-yellow-200/80">
            <strong class="text-yellow-400">Important:</strong> All content on OPX is for <strong>informational and educational purposes only</strong>. Nothing on this site constitutes medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment recommendation. Always consult a qualified healthcare professional before beginning any supplement, peptide, training program, dietary change, or other health protocol. OPX is not liable for any health decisions made based on content found on this site.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All content on the Site — including articles, graphics, logos, and design — is owned by OPX and protected by copyright law. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without explicit written permission.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Personal, non-commercial sharing (quotes with attribution, links) is permitted and encouraged.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">4. Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>
          The Site contains affiliate links. We may receive compensation when you purchase through these links. This does not influence our editorial recommendations. All affiliate relationships are disclosed in accordance with FTC guidelines.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">5. Accuracy of Information</h2>
        <p>
          We strive to provide accurate, up-to-date information. However, we make no warranties about the completeness, accuracy, or fitness for any particular purpose of the content. The wellness and health fields evolve rapidly — consult current sources and professionals for clinical decisions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, OPX shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Site or reliance on its content.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">7. External Links</h2>
        <p>
          The Site may link to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of external sites.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">8. Prohibited Use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Scrape or reproduce content for commercial use without permission</li>
          <li>Use the Site for any unlawful purpose</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Site</li>
          <li>Submit false or misleading information</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">10. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms are governed by applicable law. Any disputes shall be resolved in the appropriate jurisdiction.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@opxhq.com" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">hello@opxhq.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
